How to Use

1) Copy src/obrightness.sh to /opt folder

2) Select args from help menu: 
                       
	--plus (brightness +10%)
	--minus (brightness -10%)
	--max (brightness 100%)
	--min (brightness 0%)


3) Use command: sudo /opt/obrightness.sh --ARGS



